 (Ignore that last post, i didn't see Yanshoses last
post, S.C. And S.T. Saw Ramulus and will talk now.)

 * Shadow Cat and Snow Tech Jump in the air, suprised
by Ramulus. Wide eyed they turn to him.*

 " er, thanks. I think. Uh, We are looking for Inny, I
mean Iron Raptor. She is a long time freind of ours
and we came from our planet to look for her, when she
never came back. Uh, we see that she is kinda busy
right now, so would you please tell us of this planet?
Our computer on our ship didn't have sufficent
information on it and we don't really know much about
our beast modes either. If you would be kind enough to
show us around and explain until, Er, Iron is
finished, we would be very grateful."
